<<say $mc>> Yes, take her away please.<</say>><br>
<<say $Sheriff>>Well now, I've been itchin' to get my hands on this one. Much obliged for your service to our community.<</say>><br>
He locks eyes with $companionBandit.name, a wolfish grin spreading across his weathered face.<br><br>
<<say $Sheriff>>Here's your reward, as promised.<</say>><br>
He presses a hefty pouch of 100 dubloons into your hand, then turns his attention to "Quickfingers". Cornered, she frantically scans for an escape route, but the sheriff's iron grip closes around her arm. He begins hauling her towards the squat building behind the bounty board, her struggles futile against his determined stride.<br>
